00:32:22,674 --> 00:32:25,666
was exactly what happened
with the Beatles later on.

595
00:32:25,710 --> 00:32:27,701
It was incredible.

596
00:32:27,745 --> 00:32:32,182
Every once in a while I look on
the stage to see where he would be.

597
00:32:32,216 --> 00:32:34,207
He's not there anymore.

598
00:32:34,252 --> 00:32:36,880
So I think about
the great times we had.

599
00:32:36,921 --> 00:32:39,014
He would walk
in front of an audience

